OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start with some patchy
OL,6,Flow cloud, followed by warm sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Dry for much of the day but
OL,8,Fcloud increasing from the west with
OL,9,Frain arriving into the evening. Mild
OL,10,Ffor the time of year with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy this evening with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, mainly across
OL,14,FCumbria. Rain becoming more widespread
OL,15,Fby dawn and turning wintry over some
OL,16,Fof the hills. Breezy along the coasts
OL,17,Fand hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
