OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA damp start with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, perhaps hill snow too. Rain
OL,7,Fbecoming patchier through the
OL,8,Fafternoon but staying largely cloudy.
OL,9,FMuch cooler than Thursday, with a
OL,10,Fchilly night ahead.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry on
OL,13,FSaturday with some sunshine
OL,14,Fdeveloping. Often cloudier thereafter
OL,15,Fwith occasional patchy rain and
OL,16,Fdrizzle in places. Temperatures closer
OL,17,Fto average, with generally light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
